prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom Zen Green
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/HighJordan 1 Retro High Zoom Zen Green
prod.desciption:
Jordan Brand revamped a classic silhouette with the release of the Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom Black Green now available on StockX. Nike Zoom technology is incorporated in this design for the ultimate cushioning experience.

This Jordan 1 Retro High consists of a green suede upper with black leather overlays and an iridescent Swoosh. An icy outsole, white midsole, and Zoom branding above the Swoosh completes the design. These sneakers released in 2020 and retailed for $175.
